Bee-Fest Day 4 photo dump, Part 1 📸 🐝 

The last full day of our annual wellness retreat with a festival-vibe kept the soul fire burning! ✨ 🔥 ✨ 

Our guests tuned into the Kirtan Mantra workshop, led by @djdrez & @martinikko, and learned the beautiful stories & meanings behind the mantras. 🎶 🩵 🎵 

They got an introduction to the ELDOA Method, led by @ccrawf091 & modeled by @paigeslynchnp, which they’ll be able to apply at home for continued strength and conditioning. 💪 

Then it was time to UNLEARN LIVE, with a stirring discussion from @delbigtree on Health Freedom & Sovereignty & hosted by @cal.callahan. 🎙️ 🧠 

This transitioned into our Live Podcast Panel, with the additions of @edsbritton, @starseed.collective, @mikalvega , and @beherefarm joining Cal & Del to share their unique journeys & insights. 🙌 

Stay tuned for the Day 4, Part 2 drop and join the Bee-Fest ‘24 waitlist through our link in bio and stories! ⬆️

📸: @vickyzappegnolens

🌙✨ Dive into a world of rhythm and magic at Bhakti Fest’s LAKSHMI LOUNGE! 🎶 Experience the enchanting sounds of DJ Drez and the mesmerizing Marti Nikko as they blend mystical hip-hop, reggae roots, and Indian raga into a tapestry of musical bliss. 🌟 Let DJ Drez’s music take you from ecstatic dance to serene savasana, while Marti Nikko’s soul-soaked vocals light up the spaces with innate spark. Their chemistry, born from years of shared performances and love, creates an eclectic collection of music perfect for sacred movements and moods. 🕺🎵 Join us under the stars for an unforgettable journey! ✨Who will be joining us next month for the ultimate reunion? Passes to Bhakti Fest, September 15th - 17th are still available! We also have single day tickets for sale that are running out fast! Link in the Bio .
